{
  "title": "ISic003624. Epitaph for Zosimos",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8ENX9UZ5\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8ENX9UZ5</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρκαδείῳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρκαδείῳ\">Ἀρκαδείῳ</span></span> τὸ ε´ καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ὁνορίῳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὁνορίῳ\">Ὁνορίῳ</span></span> τὸ ε´ <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>πρὸ η´ καλανδῶν ἰουλίων <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ζώσι\n                    μος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζώσι\n                    μος\">Ζ[ώσι-]<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>μος</span></span> χρηστὸς ἐτελεύτησεν ἐ[τῶν] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>με´ ἡμέρᾳ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἄρεος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄρεος\">Ἄρεος</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8ENX9UZ5\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8ENX9UZ5</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρκαδείῳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρκαδείῳ\">ΑΡΚΑΔΕΙΩ</span></span>ΤΟΕΚΑΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ὁνορίῳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὁνορίῳ\">ΟΝΟΡΙΩ</span></span>ΤΟΕ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΠΡΟΗΚΑΛΑΝΔΩΝΙΟΥΛΙΩΝ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ζώσι\n                    μος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ζώσι\n                    μος\">Ζ[...]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΜΟΣ</span></span>ΧΡΗΣΤΟΣΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΗΣΕΝΕ[...]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΜΕΗΜΕΡΑ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἄρεος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄρεος\">ΑΡΕΟΣ</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text after Rizzone</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Orsi, Ferrua: Ὁνωρίῳ</span></span><br></li><li><span class=\"4\">4: <span>Rizzone: μ ρᾳ (presumably a typographic omission)</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>In the consulship of Arkadios for the fifth time and of Honorios for the fifth time, 8 days before the Kalend of July, worthy Zosimos passed away aged 45 years, on the day of Ares</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>Nel quinto consolato di Arcadio e nel quinto consolato di Onorio, 8 giorni prima delle calende di luglio, il buon Zosimos morì, a 45 anni, nel giorno di Ares</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1934 151 no.2 fig.21 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001697\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001697</a></li><li> Ferrua 1982-1983 no.27 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001996\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001996</a></li><li> Rizzone 2009 54 no.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001633\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001633</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-4  30  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
